## macro->has_paste to decide whether to run paste_pool_range. Lets us
## skip the pool sweep when neither body nor args contribute a `##`.
:args_have_paste
ZERO8
:emt_call_tok
ZERO8
:emt_limit
ZERO8
:emt_macro
ZERO8
:emt_saw_arg_paste
ZERO8
